IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhousto
 n.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/IMG_4987.jpeg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/upload
 s/2026/05/IMG_4987.jpeg
UID:bR8r0_EW6XiCFe6NghnLM
SUMMARY:Free Watch Party: Round of 16 (W81 vs W82)
DTSTAMP:20260701T101455Z
DTSTART:20260706T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:The first knock out round is over and the field has been cut in
	 half. Every match from here is win or go home\, and tonight someone’s Wor
	ld Cup journey ends. The Round of 16 is knockout soccer at its most raw an
	d thrilling. Be here for it! \nFestival gates open at 5:30 p.m. to the sou
	nds of DJ Athenz. Kickoff is at 7:00 p.m. Admission is free! \nFood and Be
	verage Concessions: Enjoy a variety of festival food fare\, beer and wine\
	, and non-alcoholic beverages from Coca-Cola. Visit Smalls Sliders for bur
	gers\, fries\, and shakes and cool down with Frios Gourmet Pops. Stop by H
	earsay’s festival tent for a cold beer or beer bucket or grab a michelada\
	, wine\, or beer from Gaspacho’s festival tent. Non-alcoholic drinks from 
	Coca-Cola as well as pre-packaged snacks can be purchased at the Community
	 Partner Concessions Booth\, proceeds benefiting Levy Park and the event’s
	 community partners. \nCommunity Partners: Supporting this event is the Ja
	pan-America Society of Houston. The Japan-America Society of Houston (JASH
	) is the leading organization that connects Houston’s diverse community\, 
	local businesses\, and individuals to advance the mutual interest of Ameri
	can and Japanese peoples. JASH programs in language and education\, arts a
	nd culture\, and business initiatives and networking provide opportunities
	 for collaboration and important people-to-people exchange. JASH hosts a m
	onthly program at Levy Park: Japan Junction\, as well as seasonal programm
	ing throughout the year. All proceeds from the Community Partner Concessio
	ns booth will support JASH and Levy Park. \nFace Painting & Henna Art: Get
	 into the tournament spirit with face and body art from Gio’s Art Kreation
	s and Henna Station & Glitter Bar \nMerchandise: Event merchandise celebra
	ting Houston\, Levy Park\, and the global soccer tournament will also be a
	vailable for purchase. \nArt Installations and Photo Opportunities: Commem
	orate the experience with a photo tour of the park\, including life-sized 
	soccer-themed photo backdrops and a tournament bracket. Visit our soccer b
	all music box and turn the crank for festive sounds. \nFestival Guidelines
	: \nVISITORS MUST COMPLY WITH DIRECTIONS FROM PARK PERSONNEL\, OR THEY WIL
	L BE ASKED TO LEAVE THE PARK. PARENTS ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR THEIR CHILDREN’S
	 SAFETY IN THE PARK. \nCHAIRS AND SEATING: No outside furniture. Blankets 
	may be brought into the Festival site for the designated blanket seating a
	rea. All other furniture is available on a first-come\, first-served basis
	. \nSTROLLERS & WAGONS: Oversized strollers and wagons may need to be park
	ed in a designated area during the festival. All visitors must comply with
	 park personnel regarding stroller and wagon parking. \nFOOD AND BEVERAGES
	: Guests are permitted to enter with one factory-sealed bottle of water. O
	utside food and drinks are prohibited (exceptions will be made for baby fo
	od and necessary medical dietary food items). A variety of food\, non-alco
	holic drinks\, beer\, and wine will be available for purchase from Festiva
	l concessionaires. \nRE-ENTRY: If you leave the Festival site\, you will b
	e re-screened before re-entry. \nTHE FOLLOWING ARE PROHIBITED: \n\nSmoking
	 or Vaping\nUmbrellas\nDrug Use\nKites and Drones\nRecreational Motorized 
	Vehicles\nGuns\, knives\, any weaponry\nSoliciting\nBikes\, scooters\, rol
	lerblades\, and roller skates\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/ro
	und-of-16/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/round-of-16/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT5H
END:VEVENT
